Need to run this after container is up rather than the coantainer is always in restarting mode.

sudo chown -R 1500:1500 /var/lib/docker/volumes/monitoring_influxdb_data/_data
sudo chmod -R u+rwx /var/lib/docker/volumes/monitoring_influxdb_data/_data


Use the CLI inside the InfluxDB container (or via docker exec) with:
influxdb3 create token --admin

for grafana
influxdb3 create token --permission "db:metrics:read,write" --name "GrafanaToken"

